## SS 3. Write Comment (Post Pages)

🚨 Post comments use `<textarea name="body">` (NOT contenteditable). ALWAYS `JSON.stringify()` for text.
🚨 Navigate to `{post_url}/comments` FIRST — do NOT click "Comments" button (destroys evaluate context).

**Step 0 — Navigate to comments page:**
```bash
exec curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/browser/{{browser_profile}}/navigate -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"url":"{post_url}/comments"}' 2>&1
```
Wait 3s (embed in next evaluate).

**Step 1 — Type + submit (ONE evaluate, textarea already visible):**

```bash
exec curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/browser/{{browser_profile}}/evaluate -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d @- <<'ENDJSON'
{"fn":"async () => { await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 3000)); var ta = document.querySelector('textarea[name=\"body\"]'); if (!ta) return { error: 'no comment textarea found' }; var text = COMMENT_TEXT_PLACEHOLDER; ta.focus(); ta.value = text; ta.dispatchEvent(new Event('input', { bubbles: true })); ta.dispatchEvent(new Event('change', { bubbles: true })); await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1000)); var btns = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('button')); var submitBtn = btns.find(b => b.innerText.trim() === 'Post' && !b.disabled); if (!submitBtn) { await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 2000)); btns = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('button')); submitBtn = btns.find(b => b.innerText.trim() === 'Post' && !b.disabled); } if (!submitBtn) return { typed: true, len: ta.value.length, error: 'no Post button' }; submitBtn.dispatchEvent(new MouseEvent('click', { bubbles: true, cancelable: true })); return { typed: true, submitted: true, len: ta.value.length }; }"}
ENDJSON
```

**Step 2 — Verify comment posted:**

```bash
exec curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/browser/{{browser_profile}}/evaluate -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d @- <<'ENDJSON'
{"fn":"async () => { await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 3000)); var snippet = COMMENT_SNIPPET_PLACEHOLDER; var verified = document.body.innerText.includes(snippet); return { verified: verified }; }"}
ENDJSON
```

